## Write a program to find volume of a cube

Volume of cube = `Side`^3

```txt
Side : 2

Volume : 8
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="find-volume-of-a-cube" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>

int main(void) {
  double cubeEdge = 2;
  double cubeVolume = cubeEdge * cubeEdge * cubeEdge;

  printf("Volume of cube = %f\n", cubeVolume);

  return 0;
}
```

